  "location_name": "Road through the Forest",
  "terrain": "The road is rough, uneven, and often broken with missing yellow bricks that leave holes. There are fewer houses and fruit trees along the way, and the farther they went, the more dismal and lonesome the country became. There's a little brook by the roadside where they sat down at noon.",
  "structures": "The structures are mainly farmhouses which are not well cared for. There are fewer houses in this area compared to farther back.",
  "image_prompt": "Painting of a rough, broken road scattered with yellow bricks, forming holes in some areas. Sparse, uncared-for farmhouses are scattered across the lonesome countryside. On the side of the road, a little brook is flowing."
